abstract: >-
  Public research showcase for the MirageKit program on context compression
  failure modes in large language models. The repository packages the live
  site, working-paper bundle, deterministic replay witness, and mirrored
  validation artifacts for the companion tropical-mcp evaluation
  implementation.
